<main id="content" class="content"> <header> <h1 class="title">Wonder and Concepts</h1>
 <p class="subtitle" role="doc-subtitle">Mar 09, 2015 00:00</p>
</header> <blockquote class="bigquote">
 <p>
Concepts create idols; only wonder comprehends anything. People kill one another over idols. Wonder makes us fall to our knees.
</p>
</blockquote>

 <p class="bigquote">
Gregory of Nyssa
</p>


